Interface VirtualMachine

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GroupableResource<com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute.implementation.ComputeManager,com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute.implementation.VirtualMachineInner>, HasId, HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute.implementation.VirtualMachineInner>, HasManager<com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute.implementation.ComputeManager>, HasName, HasNetworkInterfaces, HasResourceGroup, Indexable, Refreshable<VirtualMachine>, Resource, Updatable<VirtualMachine.Update>

    public interface VirtualMachine
extends GroupableResource<com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute.implementation.ComputeManager,com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute.implementation.VirtualMachineInner>, Refreshable<VirtualMachine>, Updatable<VirtualMachine.Update>, HasNetworkInterfaces
    An immutable client-side representation of an Azure virtual machine.
